metadata.name: Aurora (ETH)
metadata.description:
The clouds rise up in a measured way. There is silence all around, and only the distant chirping of thunder and cicadas in the sky reach the ears. The fresh air is brushing the skin, an intangible sensation of multidimensional distorted possibilities, a gentle sparkling dew settles on the arch. 
The steps of life lead upward, a subtle tingle of rapture in the chest... Aurora

"Aurora" is an exclusive Before You Wake inspired airdrop, created by Blank Embrace, for holders of Before You Wake.
